<section class="dress-code-section content-layer">
    <div class="dress-code-icon">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shirt"></i>
    </div>
    <h2 class="dress-code-title">Código de Vestimenta</h2>
    <p class="dress-code-subtitle">FORMAL / ELEGANTE</p>
    <p class="dress-code-quote">
        "Respetuosamente, te pedimos evitar el color púrpura y lila, ya que está
        reservado para la quinceañera."
    </p>
</section>

<style>
    .dress-code-section {
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 56rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .dress-code-icon {
        color: var(--color-accent-light);
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .dress-code-title {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--color-accent-dark);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .dress-code-subtitle {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .dress-code-quote {
        font-family: var(--font-script);
        font-size: 1.875rem;
        color: var(--color-accent-light);
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .dress-code-section {
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .dress-code-title {
            font-size: 2.75rem;
        }

        .dress-code-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .dress-code-quote {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
        }
    }
</style>
